### Component 2: Networking Module

#### [MODIFY] [main.tf](file:///c:/Users/Tan/Desktop/G9-W2/Terraform-G9/module/Networking/main.tf)

Thêm VPC Interface Endpoint cho `execute-api`:

```hcl
# VPC Interface Endpoint for API Gateway (Monitoring API private access)
resource "aws_vpc_endpoint" "apigw" {
  vpc_id              = aws_vpc.main.id
  service_name        = "com.amazonaws.${var.aws_region}.execute-api"
  vpc_endpoint_type   = "Interface"
  subnet_ids          = aws_subnet.private_app[*].id
  security_group_ids  = [var.endpoint_security_group_id]
  private_dns_enabled = true
}
```

> Endpoint gắn ở **private-app** subnets — nơi Action Group Lambda sẽ chạy.

