### Component 3: Security Module

#### [MODIFY] [main.tf](file:///c:/Users/Tan/Desktop/G9-W2/Terraform-G9/module/Security/main.tf)

Thêm 2 Security Group mới:

```hcl
# Lambda SG (Action Group + future Seed Lambda)
resource "aws_security_group" "lambda" {
  name   = "${var.project_name}-lambda-sg-${var.environment}"
  vpc_id = var.vpc_id
  egress { from_port=0; to_port=0; protocol="-1"; cidr_blocks=["0.0.0.0/0"] }
}

# VPC Endpoint SG (HTTPS 443 from Lambda)
resource "aws_security_group" "endpoint" {
  name   = "${var.project_name}-endpoint-sg-${var.environment}"
  vpc_id = var.vpc_id
  ingress { from_port=443; to_port=443; protocol="tcp"; security_groups=[aws_security_group.lambda.id] }
  egress  { from_port=0; to_port=0; protocol="-1"; cidr_blocks=["0.0.0.0/0"] }
}
```

#### [MODIFY] [outputs.tf](file:///c:/Users/Tan/Desktop/G9-W2/Terraform-G9/module/Security/outputs.tf)
- Thêm: `lambda_security_group_id`, `endpoint_security_group_id`

